import './index.scss' const SkillsBall = () => { const TagCloud = require('TagCloud') const container = '.tagcloud' const texts = [ 'HTML', 'CSS', 'JAVASCRIPT', 'SWIFT', 'MONGOOSE', 'REACT', 'PYTHON', 'SASS', 'DJANGO', 'NODEJS', 'MONGODB', 'EXPRESS', 'MYSQL', 'JQUERY', 'JAVA', ] const options = {} return (
{TagCloud(container, texts, options)}
) } export default SkillsBall
